4Geeks Academy offers a bootcamp for aspiring AI Machine Learning Engineers, designed for individuals with no prior experience. The 16-week course provides training in Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, with a focus on creating predictive models and using industry-standard tools. Students attend three classes a week, in groups of up to 12, and can choose instruction in English or Spanish. Graduates receive a recognized certificate and are equipped to tackle real-world problems in data science and machine learning. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop